"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Shell NFT is mainly used to solve the cross-game use of game equipment. \\n\\nGame developers can make special settings for certain digital content. Take Crypto Kitties as an example. Fortnite can add a certain Crypto Kitty hero. The image of the kitty in the game is not the original image of the Crypto Kitties but will be changed into the visual style of Fortnite. The game plot, value, and art will have special settings for this cat, forming a structure similar to a shell, and providing an interface, users who hold this Crypto Kitty can use their own NFT to dock with it, just like Iron Man putting on his armor. \\n\\nGenerally speaking, game developers will not make such complicated changes for a certain NFT, unless it is a legendary character, such as BAYC. \\n\\nSince we use the battle armor as the analogy, it indicates the shell also requires “energy”, which means it won’t be free to do so. After all, the virtual world is different from the real world. It is impossible to just simply transfer items between different games. Different games are like parallel universes, the worldview, the art styles, and game engines are different, and the shuttle between parallel universes inevitably consumes energy.\\n\\n \",\"timestamp\":1641145433,\"title\":\"Capsule（22.6.2021）Shell NFT \"},\"digest\":\"9PY6E3ajGbPkCF8EiXxIYNS7Q4YKTStTGAbQ_V12vKo\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xE828f8bE1a3CB994133936fB4D9A708a7D192462\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cWndKezD0ZiMgnYOqspWtyALlI_KYDziYOZaOerHeCY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Kf7VHolS02uUcQvJnvpP7ci_9wxCwvj1KsxIdy1wyS4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"EC0LxWSSj0AVL8ddcbpG_WyqRjliUcYKFeaHlKgwoRDoJ1qVJaS-rSc0iiuG3uRR0B25PX3UKXmZn98Lu8m_Pg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x24845bd906a3dcd3a6a2c8def0e1867a94aa37e04d35018a13b94099ae5be24d4b1abdd27984d765963fd65aa852fe7e1dc6d3934335a6e14328e5bca1565db21b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I 